name: INGetReservationDetailsIntentResponseCode
desc: Constants that indicate the status of the request for reservations details.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: Your app is ready to handle the intent.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: Your app is processing the request for reservation details.

items.name: case success
items.desc: Your app successfully handled the intent.

items.name: case failure
items.desc: Your app is unable to retrieve the reservation details.

items.name: case failureRequiringAppLaunch
items.desc: The user must launch your app to retrieve the reservation details.
